    <h2 class=3D"letter-title rv2 on">A letter<br><em>for Maya</em></h2>
    <textarea class=3D"letter-body rv on" placeholder=3D"Maya,

There are people who come into your life and quietly rearrange everything =
=E2=80=94 the way you see yourself, the way you let yourself be loved, the =
way you laugh without holding back.

You are that person for me.

On this birthday, I want you to know: you are not just someone I love. You =
are someone the world is genuinely better because of.

Keep being exactly, unapologetically you.

With everything,
Malak =E2=9C=A6" rows=3D"12"></textarea>
    <p class=3D"letter-sig rv on">written with love by <strong>Malak</stron=
g> =C2=B7 for <strong>Maya</strong></p>
  </div>
</section>

